                                "stop": 6.829,
                                "byte_start": 85771,
                                "byte_stop": 113147,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 98-238, West versus Gibson will be announced by Justice Breyer."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 6.829,
                        "stop": 204.156,
                        "byte_start": 113147,
